description:
It was discovered that FreeRDP incorrectly handled certain memory
operations. A remote attacker could use this issue to cause FreeRDP to
crash, resulting in a denial of service, or possibly execute arbitrary
code.

freerdp.description: RDP client for Windows Terminal Services

title: FreeRDP vulnerabilities
action: In general, a standard system update will make all the necessary changes.
isummary: Several security issues were fixed in FreeRDP.
